WEBVTT

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:30.400
and to move the agenda ahead.

00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:34.856
So, three things that I have learned
that I want to share with you

00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:36.376
through my work.

00:12:36.400 --> 00:12:42.656
One: if you want to solve
the world's biggest problems,

00:12:42.680 --> 00:12:45.896
invest in women and girls.

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:51.216
(Applause)

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:54.256
Not only do they expand the investment,

00:12:54.280 --> 00:12:56.656
but they care for everyone
in the community.

00:12:56.680 --> 00:13:00.576
Not only their needs
but the needs of their children,